BTW: This is a legendary game for a different reason too.  Gil Santos, the Voice of the Patriots in New England for 35yrs (That's Radio) and his partner of 28yrs, color man Gino Capelletti, (the first player to score in the old AFL & the All Time Scoring Leader AFL) are together again (1st qrtr only).  This drama played out on the Radio but was acknowledged briefly on the air during this broadcast.  They cut to the radio feed for the good byes and Gil's call of the last drive in the 1st.
